{
  "stem": "9102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- the way the letter is written, looking at it now-- plus, I asked my surviving aunt in Amsterdam if that-- if she remembered this writing of my father.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she says, no, it's not his.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So most likely, that is a lot of what is made up by the underground, answering my questions, basically, and just stating that, you know, keeping-- keep on hanging in there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it soon it will be over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you'll be together again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was from my father, actually, who wrote a letter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As it turned out, I was put down in the-- in the home or taken away and put in my hiding spot around the end of June.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, as far as I know from the information, got killed on July the 16th in the same year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't think they ever got the letter and know that this letter was written by them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was all done in 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What I heard after the war is my parents, being still left in the house, [? what ?] had so-called the seals on the doors.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't go out on the street anymore because nobody was supposed to know they still living there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of the neighbors in the back balcony looked after the food, brought the food over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was observed, again, by one of the other neighbors around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he kind of informed the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and one day, the whole house-- the Germans was on the roof all over-- they had gone through the neighbors, sat on the roof.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And someone knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother comes out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were just picked up and put in transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- that's what I heard after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
